    <h1><em>Disciplined</em> Rebalancing</h1>
    <div class="hero-subtitle">The Channel as Protocol</div>
    <p class="subtitle">When the Power Law channel becomes more than a model &mdash; when its bounded oscillations become triggers, and its asymmetric character becomes a discipline. Sell at percentile, rebuy at percentile, inside a wrapper that absorbs the friction. Two sentences. Observable conditions. No speculation about <em>where price is going</em>.</p>
